    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.完全关闭百度网盘PC版进程</p><p>2.使用解压工具打开C:\Users\用户名\AppData\Roaming\baidu\</p><p>BaiduNetdisk\skin\duiengineskin.zip\xml\MainPanel\NetdiskPanel\LeftPanel.xml</p><p>3.找到下列代码片段，将pos里的四个数值改为0，退出并保存</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--广告面板--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dlg</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;dlg_ad&quot;</span> <span class="attr">pos</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0,0,0,0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">show</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--与AdPanel.xml内容一致--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：百度网盘PC版更新后，需重新修改</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
