  <entry>
    <title>AdobeFlashPlayer安装步骤</title>
    <link href="https://timhliu.me/posts/3564.html"/>
    <id>https://timhliu.me/posts/3564.html</id>
    <published>2020-09-23T10:28:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-24T05:26:47.962Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-下载Flash国际版离线安装包"><a href="#1-下载Flash国际版离线安装包" class="headerlink" title="1.下载Flash国际版离线安装包"></a>1.下载Flash国际版离线安装包</h2><h3 id="Internet-Explorer-ActiveX-for-XP-和-Win7"><a href="#Internet-Explorer-ActiveX-for-XP-和-Win7" class="headerlink" title="Internet Explorer - ActiveX(for XP 和 Win7)"></a>Internet Explorer - ActiveX(for XP 和 Win7)</h3><p><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ax.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ax.exe</a><br><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ax.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ax.exe</a></p><h3 id="Firefox-NPAPI"><a href="#Firefox-NPAPI" class="headerlink" title="Firefox - NPAPI"></a>Firefox - NPAPI</h3><p><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player.exe</a><br><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player.exe</a></p><h3 id="Chrome-和其它基于-Chromium-的浏览器-PPAPI"><a href="#Chrome-和其它基于-Chromium-的浏览器-PPAPI" class="headerlink" title="Chrome 和其它基于 Chromium 的浏览器 - PPAPI"></a>Chrome 和其它基于 Chromium 的浏览器 - PPAPI</h3><p><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ppapi.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ppapi.exe</a><br><a href="https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ppapi.exe">https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/get/flashplayer/latest/help/install_flash_player_ppapi.exe</a></p><h2 id="2-断网安装离线安装包"><a href="#2-断网安装离线安装包" class="headerlink" title="2.断网安装离线安装包"></a>2.断网安装离线安装包</h2><h2 id="3-替换破解文件"><a href="#3-替换破解文件" class="headerlink" title="3.替换破解文件"></a>3.替换破解文件</h2><p>32位系统，将32位文件替换到 C:\Windows\System32\Macromed\Flash 下覆盖同名文件</p><p>64位系统，先将2个32位文件替换到 C:\Windows\SysWOW64\Macromed\Flash 下覆盖同名文件，再将剩下的那个64位文件替换到 C:\Windows\System32\Macromed\Flash 下覆盖同名文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">三种类型的 Flash 破解文件一共有9个，分别是：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ActiveX类型：Flash32_**_0_0_***.ocx、Flash64_**_0_0_***.ocx、FlashUtil32_**_0_0_***_ActiveX.exe</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">NPAPI类型：FlashUtil32_**_0_0_***_Plugin.exe、NPSWF32_**_0_0_***.dll、NPSWF64_**_0_0_***.dll</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">PPAPI类型：FlashUtil32_**_0_0_***_pepper.exe、pepflashplayer32_**_0_0_***.dll、pepflashplayer64_**_0_0_***.dll</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-注意事项"><a href="#4-注意事项" class="headerlink" title="4.注意事项"></a>4.注意事项</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">4.1 替换 ActiveX 版 ocx 文件时会提示“目标文件夹访问被拒绝，您需要权限来进行此操作”，请在原版文件上右键-属性-安全-高级-权限-更改权限-把拒绝的权限项目全都删掉</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4.2 Windows 8.1&#x2F;10 不需要安装 ActiveX 版 Flash 安装包，For Windows 10 的 Edge 和 For Windows 8.1&#x2F;10 的 IE 的嵌入式的 ActiveX 版 Flash 是通过系统补丁的方式推送安装的，这样安装的 Flash 插件没有区域限制问题，所以无须替换</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4.3 Chrome 和其它基于 Chromium 的浏览器，请直接使用“Adobe Flash Player PPAPI **.0.0.*** for Chromium”直接替换文件，路径是 浏览器的 User Data\PepperFlash 下的 manifest.json 和 pepflashplayer.dll</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4.4 **.0.0.***指的是 Flash 的版本号，如果使用的是CentBrowser，则不需要套这个版本号文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
